+== Installation
+
+You need RubyGems[http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=126].
+
+ % gem install coderay
+
+
+=== Dependencies
+
+CodeRay needs Ruby 1.8.6 or later. It should also run with Ruby 1.9 and JRuby.
+
